purpose: Hi, this is just a quick test call. I wanted to check if the interruption feature is working. Try interrupting me anytime!

messages.content: I need to have a quick question.
Oh sure, go ahead! What's your question?

I'm running on Claude - it's Anthropic's AI model. But honestly, the main thing I wanted to test here is whether you can interrupt me while I'm speaking. So if I just keep talking for a bit, feel free to jump in anytime and cut me off - that's actually what we're trying to test out today!
Perfect! So the interruption feature is working on your end - that's exactly what we needed to know. I'll let Naveen know the test was successful. Thanks for helping us out with this!
